&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2–4 years of experience in Workforce Management, Operations, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foundational understanding of workforce planning concepts including forecasting, capacity planning, and staffing analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Excel; exposure to Power BI or similar data visualization tools is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
